THISDAY business correspondent, Nation’s Capital, Mr. James Emejo has lost his biological mother, Princess Ogbu Egah Comfort (Nee Ukoro) who died on October 29, 2018, after a protracted illness at the age of 70. She is survived by children, grandchildren, sisters and brothers. . According to the burial arrangement, the body leaves Last Home Mortuary, Avarichi for a Wake Keep at her residence, Ogbu’s Compound Ndogagba- Oloche 1, Utonkon, Benue State, on Friday, November 23, 2018 On Saturday, November 24, 2018, her body departs her residence to Udebo Cemetery, Utonkon for interment.